title: This New Video Will Get You Amped for the Ronda Rousey-Holly Holm Fight
text: Every superhero has an origin story. Ronda Rousey is no exception. And neither is her next opponent Holly Holm , who hasn’t reached superhero status —but would, if she managed to take out the undefeated queen on MMA on November 14. With the fight just over a month away, a slickly-produced hype video has arrived to get your hairs standing on end. It traces the journeys of Rousey and Holm from young, ostracized fighters to mature, intimidating forces. A little bit of trivia: That girl playing a teenage Rousey looks a lot like Ronda for a reason. It's her 15-year-old sister Julia.
